narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: Resources were excellent. Maybe a reading list at the beginning of the semester would help. More money for materials is always helpful since $200 is pretty unrealistic.
Resources were adequate. I enjoyed every minute I spent in the Shop working on this project.
